{"id": 3078, "genre": 1001, "title": "啥样的日常细节会让你觉得“自己对生活有掌控感”？", "description": "你都是从哪些不起眼的迹象中，找到自己的生活秩序的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 1359, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201912030018475PWN6Yd9l7IGBJip.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-02T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 349952, "content": "每天冥想一会，心情会放松很多 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673260}, {"id": 349953, "content": "按时早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717311}, {"id": 349954, "content": "在有阳光洒进的空间里，读喜欢的书听喜爱的音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673268}, {"id": 349955, "content": "自己的时间自己能把握", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244251}, {"id": 349956, "content": "早上可以自己做三明治，不去吃食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419788}, {"id": 349957, "content": "自律", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497088}, {"id": 349958, "content": "做自己想做的事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434148}, {"id": 349960, "content": "也许是在某一刹那意识到，我才是我宇宙的中心。我平凡但我也也是自己世界的王", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463151}, {"id": 349961, "content": "在外面一个人散心的时候，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668209}, {"id": 349963, "content": "有时间做自己喜欢做的事，阅读，思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673056}, {"id": 349964, "content": "骑自行车去某地，不会堵车，想快就快，想慢就慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915935}, {"id": 349965, "content": "下班比平时早", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495957}, {"id": 349966, "content": "完成To do list上的任务", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413986}, {"id": 349967, "content": "和朋友每周约一次饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588326}, {"id": 349969, "content": "有太阳的日子可以晒太阳", "image": "img/option/option/20191203150722fFWX0d31eVJ7NkMD.jpg", "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601494}, {"id": 349970, "content": "洗发水牙膏卫生纸用完之后有存货可以续上", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530398}, {"id": 349971, "content": "每天更新自己的bujo，我感觉我自己掌握了自己的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 16540}, {"id": 350227, "content": "有独处的时间，能做自己喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366724}, {"id": 349972, "content": "早起，按时吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673324}, {"id": 350228, "content": "不用匆匆忙忙赶地铁的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631549}, {"id": 349973, "content": "晚睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106418}, {"id": 349975, "content": "准时睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668570}, {"id": 349976, "content": "拥有几个特别稳定的朋友，每天有一段可以放空自己的时间，在清单上罗列当天需要做的事情，早起，吃早餐，收拾屋子，洗澡，洗衣服，晚上躺床上就睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662606}, {"id": 349977, "content": "慎独", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648526}, {"id": 349978, "content": "知道明天有事做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672908}, {"id": 349979, "content": "下班回到出租屋还能躺下的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20191203171203LN5BWh7loeAcuYCE.png", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374022}, {"id": 349982, "content": "有空看好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259801}, {"id": 349983, "content": "口袋有零钱，发现零钱唔够买喜欢的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446964}, {"id": 349985, "content": "宿舍四个人，每次自己没有时间时，聚会一般都改期。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500599}, {"id": 349986, "content": "早上闹钟响了能爬起来 晚上关了灯能睡得着", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673361}, {"id": 349988, "content": "钱包有余额", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227146}, {"id": 349994, "content": "很早起来，也许是天还没亮的时候，大街上没有人，我一个人漫步在街上，看着太阳慢慢升起，感觉全世界都是我的！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672393}, {"id": 349997, "content": "喜欢有喜欢的人\n在此中焦虑欣喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511972}, {"id": 350000, "content": "写一首自我感觉还凑合的小诗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572865}, {"id": 350003, "content": "和家人多人共享同步的iCloud日历", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560150}, {"id": 350004, "content": "心情好才收拾屋子，就算乱了也没人管。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 350005, "content": "能按自己的计划完成所有事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673399}, {"id": 350007, "content": "压腿抻筋，伸展身体", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660293}, {"id": 350008, "content": "每天能够在完成工作的情况下有时间练字➕阅读➕写日记。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274409}, {"id": 350009, "content": "吃点啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673444}, {"id": 350010, "content": "可以静下心干一件事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673461}, {"id": 351546, "content": "将安排的日程过完时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 350011, "content": "洗衣服，每天晚上手搓着衣服就觉得我活的很认真。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213780}, {"id": 350012, "content": "每天早上打开衣柜知道今天要穿啥，有衣服穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673417}, {"id": 350017, "content": "刷手机刷到深夜第二天早上自然醒然后去做早午餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461025}, {"id": 351556, "content": "当我提早到公司，在上班前我还有时间学习，或者只是一篇文章或者一个音频", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506438}, {"id": 350022, "content": "想吃什么自己都能做出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355256}, {"id": 350030, "content": "想了很久，竟然发现没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588249}, {"id": 352335, "content": "思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350036, "content": "无论哪个方面，把需要做的事情提前做好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673528}]}